  <div class="unit how">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <div class="unit_illustration":>
      <!-- <h3>How it works</h3> -->
      <%= image_tag "canary-map.medium.png" %>
    </div>
    <div class="unit_exposition">
      <h3>How it works</h3>
      <p>
        We keep track of which versions of what packages are vulnerable to which security vulnerabilities, so you don't have to.</p>
      <p>
        We provide an <a href="https://github.com/appcanary/agent">open-source</a> agent and an API. We monitor the packages you have installed on your Linux system by hooking into the package manager (i.e. apt or yum). We also monitor the libraries used by your Ruby applications by monitoring their Gemfile.lock files.
