      </p>
      <p>
        <!-- We provide an <a href="https://github.com/appcanary/agent">open&#45;source</a> agent and an API. Our APIs support the same platforms as the agent. You can monitor a set of packages for vulnerabilities by uploading a file, either a Gemfile.lock for Ruby or <code>/var/lib/dpkg/status</code> for apt&#45;based systems, or the output of <code>rpm &#45;qa</code> for rpm&#45;based systems. -->
      </p>
      <p>
        You can upload files directly to our API endpoint, or through a web
